fields.title: Enter the Void
fields.body: Let go your earthly tether. Enter the void. Empty, and become wind.

fields.title: When Harry Met Sally
fields.body: Wait a second, wait a, wait a second. What are you doing for New Years? Are you going to the Tyler's party? 'Cos I don't have a date, and if you don't have a date, we always said that if neither one of us had a date, we could be together for New Years

fields.title: Lollipop
fields.body: Lollipop lollipop. Oh lolli lolli lolli, lollipop.
